burlap.domain.singleagent.blockdude

Class BlockDudeLevelConstructor

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.domain.singleagent.blockdude.BlockDudeLevelConstructor

  • public class BlockDudeLevelConstructor
extends Object
    A class for generating the initial states for BlockDude from levels in the classic Block Dude game. Currently this class will provide the initial states for the first three levels of Block Dude.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
